videos.headline: NaLyssa Smith's nice kick-out pass leads to Sarah Andrews' 3-pointer for Baylor
videos.description: NaLyssa Smith avoids the pressure down low and kicks it out to Sarah Andrews for a 3-pointer in the first quarter.
